        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Medicare Safe Needle Disposal Coverage Act of 2015</b></p> <p> Amends part D (Voluntary Prescription Drug Benefit Program) of title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to cover as a part D drug any devices approved for home use by the Food and Drug Administration for the safe and effective containment, removal, decontamination, and disposal of home-generated needles, syringes, and other sharps through a sharps container, decontamination/destructive device, or sharps-by-mail program or similar program.</p>]]></text>
